The '''XRCO Hall of Fame''' lists some of the most notable [[adult entertainment]] works and workers. The list is managed by [[X-Rated Critics Organization]] and inducted annually during the [[XRCO Award]]s. The first XRCO Awards were presented in Hollywood on February 14, 1985.<ref>[http://www.dirtybob.com/xrco/ XRCO] home page</ref> Inductees must have been industry members for at least ten years.<ref name="XRCO website">{{cite web|url=http://www.xrco.com|title=XRCO|accessdate=14 January 2014}}</ref>
